description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Glute and Core Burner Circuit' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other and Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Fire up your lower body with Pete as you tackle exercises aimed at improving your glute, leg, and core strength, with a mini-band and foam roller. Max rhythm: 30, Format: Circuit ...
